# Important Changes

# Requirements Update (requirements will need to be reinstalled)
Bump plexapi to 4.18.1
Bump python-dotenv to 1.2.2
Bump pillow to 12.1.1
Bump requests to 2.33.0
Bump setuptools to 82.0.1

# New Features
Switching to using GraphQL for IMDB charts retrieval, with a fallback to the old method if the GraphQL request fails. #3006
Adds new `text_file` builder.
Reciperr site hasn't responded for a while, so the builder has been removed.
Added spellcheck to precommit configuration

# Docs

# Defaults
Ratings Default file now fetches the rating during the Run, meaning users no longer have to rely on Plex's rating system or use the Mass Rating Update operations in order to get rating overlays.
Ratings Default file will now auto-pick the best image if one is not selected. For example, if `rating1: imdb` then the pre-configured `rating1_image` will be `imdb` out of the box without the user having to specify.

# Bug Fixes
Catch KeyError on Plex NFO build.
Fixing "list index out of range" error when processing imdb charts #3006
Reduce size of FILMIN logo
Replace top-ten-pirated default list with an updated, kometa-controlled one.
